                                                                                              outcomes with mission or business requirements, risk tolerance, and resources of the organization. 59 The
                                                                                              prioritized list of cybersecurity outcomes developed at the organization and mission/business process
                                                                                              levels can be helpful in facilitating consistent, risk-based decisions at the system level. The Subcategories
                                                                                              identified in the applicable Cybersecurity Framework Profiles can also be used to guide and inform the
                                                                                              development of the tailored control baselines described above.
